❤️‍🔥  ARAFTA DİZİ ÖZETİ (KUMA - Türk Dizileri'da)

Kaderin Bağladığı
İki kalp. Bir seçim. Aşk mı kazanır, intikam mı?

Türkiye’nin büyüleyici manzaraları fonunda Arafta, öfkenin ateşiyle aşkın sessiz çağrısının çarpıştığı bir hikâyeyi anlatır. Geçmişinin yaralarıyla yüzleşen Ateş, hesap sormak için geri döndüğünde bütün dengeler değişir. Mercan ise kaderin sürüklediği bu dünyada kalbini korumaya çalışırken, güven ve şüphe arasında ince bir çizgide yürür. Gölgelere saklanan sırlar, susulan sözler ve yakıcı bir çekim… Arafta, her adımda “kalp mi, gurur mu?” sorusunu yeniden sorduran, tutku ve hesaplaşmanın büyüyen gerilimi.

ARAFTA - Bound by Fate
Two hearts. One choice. Will love or revenge win?

Set against the stunning backdrop of Turkey's landscapes, Arafta tells a story where the fire of anger collides with the silent call of love.In Arafta, with every step, the question "heart or pride?" The growing tension of passion and reckoning that makes one ask the question again.

snippet.title: Anime “Dragon Ball Super: Beerus” | SUPER Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

◾️INTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media—from TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising—standing as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga—bringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus’s overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear… Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza—and suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies—a conflict that will shake the entire universe.

-- Lyrics --

Ya Abbas Ya Abbas x4

Is se zahir hai jahan par tera rutba Abbas
Khud Ali ne bhi kayi baar kah Ya Abbas

1. Jab Nabi ne kaha Hasnain mere bete hain
Fatima Zahra pukaareen Mera beta Abbas

Muskura kar kaha: Saqqa-e-Sakina Abbas

Ban gayi mashk-e-Sakina tera tamgha Abbas

‎خود علیؑ نے بھی کئی بار کہا یا عباسؑ

‎جب نبیؐ نے کہا حسنؑ و حسینؑ میرے بیٹے ہیں
‎فاطمہؑ زہراؑ پکاریں میرا بیٹا عباسؑ

‎پوچھا عباسؑ سے جب اُن کا پسندیدہ لقب
‎مسکرا کر کہا سقّائے سکینہؑ عباسؑ

آپ کی قبر کے گرد اب بھی ہے مصروفِ طواف
آپ کے قبضے میں ہے آج بھی دریا عباس

‎لگتا ہے ساتھ نکل آئے ہیں چاند اور سورج
‎ دیکھ کر آپ کا اور شاہ کا روضہ عباس

‎ہاتھ والوں نے بھی اُتنا نہیں تقسیم کیا
‎آپ نے جتنا کٹے ہاتھوں سے بانٹا عباس

‎تجھ کو جُرأت پہ ملا سب سے بڑا یہ انعام
‎بن گئی مشکِ سکینہؑ تیرا تمغہ عباسؑ

‎لوگ توحیدِ علیؑ میں نہ کریں شرک کہیں
‎ڈھانپ لیتے تھے یہی سوچ کے چہرہ عباسؑ

‎بن گئے حضرتِ عباس کے میثم ثقلین 
‎دار پر جاکے بھی ہم بولیں گے مولا عباس
